#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:5
msgid "Vale of Tears"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:141
msgid ""
"We have followed you away from our homes and left them unguarded.  Now, "
"where can we find this sage who knows the southern forest well?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:146
msgid ""
"This is the Vale of Blossoming Trees.  Our great sages come here to live "
"when they feel that it is time for them to allow others to lead our people.  "
"The sage you speak of lives in a secluded village between the two lakes."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:151
msgid ""
"Why, my lady, are there humans camped to the south of us?  Are they friends "
"of the elves?  I had thought that no humans had set foot in this valley."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:156
msgid ""
"What!?  Those are no friends of the elves!  They are brigands, and they must "
"be destroyed!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:161
msgid ""
"Perhaps they are allied with the bandits who have been sacking out towns!  "
"They have grown bold to attack the elves!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:166
msgid ""
"Destroy these intruders, and I will ask him to help you.  He is ancient, and "
"he remembers well Haldric's betrayal of the elves, so if a human sets foot "
"in his village first, he almost certainly will have nothing to do with us!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:171
msgid "Sounds like a charming fellow..."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:176
msgid ""
"Yet, as she says, he is our best hope to rid our lands of this new menace.  "
"We do that which we must.  Ethiliel, you make for Mebrin's village.  We will "
"handle the intruders."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Ha! You're too late.  We've taken what we want from this valley.  Now your "
"blood and tears will join that of the elves!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:187
msgid "Cleanse the Vale of Tears"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:191
msgid "Move Ethiliel to Mebrin's village"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:195
msgid "Death of Deoran"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:199
msgid "Death of Sir Gerrick"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:203
msgid "Death of Ethiliel"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:207
msgid "Time runs out"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:228
msgid ""
"Our weapons are useless against these skeletons!  They have nothing for our "
"shafts to pierce but air!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:232
msgid ""
"We must clear out these undead if you are to reach Mebrin's village!  What "
"should we do?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:237
msgid ""
"For now, I can slow them down.  Where are the elves who used to live in this "
"valley?  They should come to our aid!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:242
msgid ""
"You said this valley would be safe, and we find it filled with skeletal "
"foes!  Cannot some of your elf friends help us in our struggle?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:256
msgid "I shall not join these accursed undead!  Bury me deeply my friends..."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:261
msgid "You shall not die in vain!  My bodyguard will avenge you!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:266
msgid "You have a bodyguard?!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:271
msgid "You have a bodyguard?!!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:344
msgid ""
"We stand ready, my lady, to protect you!  We shall lead these men of Wesnoth "
"into the fray!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:357
msgid "For my lady I fall..."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:370
msgid "Finally, release!  Thank you, my friends..."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:416
msgid ""
"You're too late!  You'll never find our stronghold, and even if you did, "
"what can you do against the dead!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:421
msgid "You, at least, will trouble us no more!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:468
msgid "Mebrin! Are you there?  We have come to seek your aid!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:473
#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:483
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:478
msgid "Mebrin! Where are you?!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:488
msgid ""
"His home is empty...  There are footprints leading away to the south...  "
"What can have happened here?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:493
msgid "Maybe whoever summoned these undead knows where he is?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:498
msgid ""
"There is no blood here, yet no Mebrin.  Someone must have kidnapped him.  "
"But the undead would have slain him and made him one of them.  Who then can "
"have taken him?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:503
msgid "Maybe the bandits who have been summoning the undead took him?"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:508
msgid ""
"We must follow these footprints into the woods!  Whoever took our greatest "
"sage must pay!  Nothing will stop the vengeance of the elves!"
msgstr ""

#: The_South_Guard/scenarios/4.Valley_of_Tears.cfg:513
msgid ""
"Well, vengeance or no, if you will lead us into the forest, we will follow "
"you and battle the undead!"
msgstr ""
